Introduction

JooBin is a South Korean singer under MODHAUS.

On December 22, 2023, JooBin was introduced as the eighteenth member of the girl group tripleS under MODHAUS. She first released the single "Just Do It" as part of the sub-unit NXT, before officially debuting with tripleS on May 8, 2024, with the album "ASSEMBLE24".

As a member of tripleS, JooBin was placed in the sub-unit NXT.
